data.title: Edwin O. Smith High School: Revenue, Competitors, Alternatives
data.meta_description: Edwin O. Smith High School top competitors are Coventry Board Of Education, New Beginnings Family Academy and Yale Science Technology and Research Scholars and they have annual revenue of $48.3M  and 244  employees.
data.text:
E.O Smith High School offers students a wide breadth of education to prepare them for the future. We host active academic departments, an agricultural training program, and a number of student clubs and extra-curricular activities.
